# See https://github.com/nektos/act#configuration for more options
# This basic file helps act select a default image.

# For Linux runners - using a valid image that exists
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest

# For macOS runners (often needs specific architecture for Docker):
# -P macos-latest=nektos/act-environments-macos:latest

# Container architecture for Apple Silicon Macs
--container-architecture linux/amd64

# You can also specify a default image for all jobs if not specified in workflow:
# --default-image nektos/act-environments-ubuntu:latest 